不理智行動<br />\n搞到連班港豬同淺藍都怕咗我地<br />\n從而令對家加強返作為執法者嘅認受性(雖然加強完都係負數)<br />\n<br />\n一定要好好建立返好前線/運動形象<br />\n勇武手足行動時真係要有返d Pr意識<br />\n好似初期個班高質前線做d野全部恰到好處<br />\n對準政權又與民為善,去到邊都受到歡呼<br />\n呢樣先最令對家措手不及同應對唔到<br />\n佢唔鎮壓你佢輸,佢鎮壓你再輸多幾錢重"},{"pid":"be4b0e2238a80c548c1265a55f75596936da39bb","tid":1801553,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c695f182d0fd0297740adfc0a6dee3038d5ae293","tid":1801553,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"827c784663a81b636c9bba180f0295c97f964226","tid":1801553,"uid":68944,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ac6e755ed10b189eb1560787716b23ca350d5b85","tid":1801553,"uid":125516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"咁荃灣俾人斬嘅手足就抵死？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:37:40.000Z","msg":"我明你擔心乜嘢，不過事實係你唔洗擔心，到呢個地步，放火燒人唔會有任何影響，一個人如果會因為自己人行使戰爭權力而退卻，說明呢個人本身都冇乜行動力，唔使理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:55:17.000Z","msg":"放火燒人都冇任何影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7a4798606d8ec460c2117a8de6e8303e44069d","tid":1801553,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e71ee58f0a963b293998bd006704f5bd8af0df6","tid":1801553,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:57:44.000Z","msg":"[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥) (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801519</a><br />\n<br />\n上水和你shop聽日仲有<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801500</a>"},{"pid":"c2c78b4e1275dfc4e0a6948cd821c28fa100e6d1","tid":1801553,"uid":248587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T18:00:09.000Z","msg":"去到今時今日你都仲唔可以接受到係